rmal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者討論下其實香港需要咩訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"8月5日全港齊心大罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378023</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n齊心一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入黎一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月5號一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebf60338cdaf40ede499f17fcdf50db0803d914","tid":1378360,"uid":264914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1876ed6c82fd3f4c23fb5e6538d0a66ff01c5938","tid":1378360,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c82cc4df23528c9bae38981b2ebdab1ccb9163e7","tid":1378360,"uid":264914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89b17698287472ef2fa557eed89d78bfc43bb7d4","tid":1378360,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"政治人才呢點，講真，嘔返市政局出黎就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"巴打，我90後孤陋寡聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />岩岩wiki先知市政局99年比老董廢左，想知點解你覺得整番市政局幫倒手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk/127_hist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk%2F127_hist%2F&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=642c6f24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk/127_hist/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:43:59.000Z","msg":"睇完再次覺得政府好狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無錯我覺得我地要爭取呢D，看似比較無害，但又改善倒政治環境既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8633eddb83e1f6301f33850eb3b04c472c3e0ef","tid":1378360,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c3cba248db3c697aeba8077fa9b130ead903fc","tid":1378360,"uid":264914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:02:40.000Z","msg":"唔好比個運動失去意義，我地宜家有本錢同政府飛禽大咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c603abc81d5a93c7a70261d9fda8436c73e0015","tid":1378360,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"郭家麒: 暴力既源頭係林鄭政府，造成今日既亂局係有中央政府包庇林鄭同警隊 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1380805/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1380805/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"282224963cb40e22e15d65561ec67053e6fd3fde","tid":1378360,"uid":264914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3e31ef7b23bf775f44bda691c7497c3f90f10f","tid":1378360,"uid":264914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:37:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}